@model BAL.Models.AmendmentDetailsMessageImlementationModel
@using (Html.BeginForm("AddUpdateAmendmentDetailsMessageImplementation", "AmendmentDetailsMessageImplementation", FormMethod.Post, new { @id = "frmAmendmentDetailsMessageImplementation" }))
{
    <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title">Add/Update Amendment Details</h4>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        @Html.HiddenFor(z => z.iMessageImplementationId)
        @Html.HiddenFor(z => z.iAmendmentId)
        <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col-md-4">
                @Html.LabelFor(z => z.sAmendRefNo)
                @Html.TextBoxFor(z => z.sAmendRefNo, new { @class = "form-control" })
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(z => z.sAmendRefNo)
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-md-4">
                @Html.LabelFor(z => z.sAmendFlag)
                @Html.TextBoxFor(z => z.sAmendFlag, new { @class = "form-control" })
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(z => z.sAmendFlag)
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-md-4">
                @Html.LabelFor(z => z.sAmendType)
                @Html.TextBoxFor(z => z.sAmendType, new { @class = "form-control" })
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(z => z.sAmendType)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Submit</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
    </div>
}
